Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:03.94,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:05.56,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:12.11,Brave-Main,IZANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I shall destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.07,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.62,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.77,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:44.64,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.87,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't get up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:50.61,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, this darkness... \NIs this Isanami's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:55.95,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,We must act before the darkness \Nconsumes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:00:59.45,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.19,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You're not fit to move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.93,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Troubling you would be the greatest \Ndishonor as your servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:10.67,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can still see the prophecy of\NIzumo that was engraved in my lost eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:14.89,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:17.63,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:21.20,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.06,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.02,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:38.78,Ep-Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,The Warrior of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.95,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:48.39,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,This foreboding atmosphere is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.65,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:55.66,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Is she the goddess of death with the\Ndark power to destroy the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.72,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.68,Brave-Main,IZANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:00.85,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.99,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My dark self is growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.00,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.25,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a control device.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:13.90,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,With the Kushimitama, I should \Nbe able to bend her to my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.57,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hanzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.42,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you're desperate to \Nrecover the Kushimitama,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.95,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,but what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.53,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not trying to kill me,\Nyou don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:34.23,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,This is where your \Nlukewarm team gets you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:39.47,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Your desire for nice little \Nfriendships makes you weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.52,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja's only ally is himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.74,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,You can only count on your own ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.68,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,your own body, your own senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.45,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,You think someone who has forgotten\Nthese things can fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:53.90,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.48,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:02.28,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What can a man who only thinks \Nof himself do with that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.70,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:10.21,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do far more than a fool who doesn't\Neven attempt to use such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.92,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think only of myself, \Nmy actions are pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:18.55,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this power is too great for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.21,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,You have none of the exceptional \Nqualities of a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.91,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Truly irresolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.89,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,It is your fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:30.85,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,The ease with which the ice infiltrated\Nyour defenses speaks to your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.47,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a generous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:37.68,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,That woman took my bait \Nhook, line, and sinker,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.72,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,while spouting idealistic nonsense about \Nthe restoration of her homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.07,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,She played her part well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.48,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose she was a useful tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.98,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your damn mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:55.00,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Ana was never your tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:59.96,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,She was putting her life on the \Nline for what she believed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.43,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you'd never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.81,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.98,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well be shouting at nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:20.11,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch from down there as the\Ndarkness falls under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.24,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.95,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,She will do anything I teach her to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.03,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Pure destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.58,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for a man of pure desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.63,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.63,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isana...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.29,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.02,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I have the Kushimitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.55,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,She should obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.94,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness will consume me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.72,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It rejected Hanzo...\Nand the Kushimitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:18.76,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.16,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.17,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,The prophecy under Izumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.93,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,"When the power of darkness rises again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.64,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,dispel it with the lives \Nof the nine elements."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.74,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.64,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,The prophecy of Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.70,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the inscription?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.92,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my right eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:48.57,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,but I am still one of the \Nwarriors of the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:54.29,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,If my life will do anything \Nto stop the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.74,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:57.00,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:02.21,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive this final \Nact of disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.35,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.17,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro, Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:25.78,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to stop this \Ndarkness with our lives, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.78,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.38,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, you saw what happened to Hanzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:38.49,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't Isanami any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:41.11,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Act carelessly, and it \Nwill destroy you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.21,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:47.17,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Acting without thinking and \Ncausing nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:52.18,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,She's grown into a bigger form,\Nbut nothing else has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.22,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.39,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let that bullshit rule me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.07,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:06.82,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut open that darkness \Nand bring her out my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.00,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.45,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.91,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:22.58,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:29.26,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,United by our common identity as braves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.68,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,we could face any opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.30,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's our true strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:42.48,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about fate, \Nand I don't care either,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.73,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,but because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:49.50,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we rallied around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.61,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:57.22,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, we'll always be one short!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.00,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.63,Brave-Main,YOKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo has...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.09,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:17.01,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you really want, Isanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.44,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Isa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.23,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,The gods will save mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:25.69,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, those who serve \Nthe gods will save men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.86,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be so arrogant, Seikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.69,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,Even the gods cannot do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.98,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:37.16,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Buddhists, \Nchanting invocations alone will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:41.71,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,No good will come from staying \Nin this narrow-minded shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.05,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.83,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I will find the true \Nmeaning of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.93,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.03,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.18,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.05,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's already dark. It's scary outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.14,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.01,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here and wait like a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.25,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Bring me back presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.18,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,She was smiling then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.67,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that smile would \Nalways stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.78,Brave-Italic,VILLAGER A,0000,0000,0000,,What a disaster. Is everyone dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.60,Brave-Italic,VILLAGER B,0000,0000,0000,,No, I heard one of the \Npriestesses survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.64,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I must find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.95,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I must teach her, now that I \Nhave achieved enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.59,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami is waiting for me with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.71,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.33,Brave-Italic,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I believed in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.84,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.82,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me. Give me a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.72,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:44.84,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,The gods I believed in \Nhave abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.28,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Then believe in your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.75,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.66,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,If we work together, \Nshe doesn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:52.61,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:56.93,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Benmaru Special Explosive, \NHinokagutsuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:57.86,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:01.11,Brave-Main,BYAKUGUN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to die, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.34,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.84,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.32,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness is confusing the insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.12,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.68,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.56,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,This ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.31,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Koga Hi-Ougi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.71,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Mangokusatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.75,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,How weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.48,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that would \Nbe enough to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.40,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Move, and it will cut deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.66,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.41,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.72,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,My face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.08,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,My face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.05,Brave-Main,KAIO,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.98,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.81,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Let me put you out of your misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:04.18,Brave-Main,KUCHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you the pain you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.56,Brave-Main,KUCHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you can hear me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.54,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this way in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.78,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:27.23,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,This red world is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.91,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.88,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.84,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:43.26,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.35,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hekireki Hoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.36,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Shocking, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:59.06,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Not knowing my abilities \Nwas your undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.77,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking your ice was no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.54,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Was the jolt too much for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.42,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've lost too much \Nblood to get it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.66,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.28,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're pretty warm after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.24,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.39,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you'll return, Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.10,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.60,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,This thing hasn't lost its power, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.53,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.45,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.98,Brave-Main,IZANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:45.99,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.52,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Then what're you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:50.45,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.33,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.07,Brave-Main,IZANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I will take a thousand lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.48,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.46,Brave-Main,IZANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I will take them again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.20,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.43,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:05.39,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can only hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.35,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is full of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.14,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NOf course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.02,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's got some \Ndarkness in their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:18.16,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're not any different!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.98,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I cause everyone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:27.20,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,So what? I've gotten used \Nto it since meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.91,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:36.10,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring on the forceful personality \Nand ridiculous fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.42,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run from them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.84,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.59,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My heart hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.55,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart hurts because you're human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.01,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember what you told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.50,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd always believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.07,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You sounded like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.81,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.82,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a human \Nor some goddess of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.69,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're just you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.86,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.13,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the ten braves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:11.17,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.83,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.51,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, Isanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.66,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.12,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.80,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.41,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.72,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:10.26,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.14,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:16.43,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.25,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.39,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.61,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.25,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.53,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.68,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.20,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.88,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,How ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.99,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it was fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.76,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:57.75,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can move so \Nsoon after taking my bolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.76,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,You're chasing me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.23,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:04.70,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.67,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind letting you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.99,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.70,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo and Sasuke would \Nnever forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.16,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean the lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:21.12,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I don't think \Neven he'd forgive this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.58,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:29.76,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,I have no regrets, but my dream is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.63,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:37.49,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing left? Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:43.40,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,When you have nothing left, \Nyou're free to do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.35,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a chance to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:48.07,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,So? What're you gonna do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.84,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.36,Brave-Main,ANASTASIA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to do something \Nabout how terrible I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.58,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,A dark power to consume everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:03.80,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Even if such a power exists, \Nwe should not seek it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:11.01,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,Ieyasu must truly be a fool \Nto want such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:16.47,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,However, we must do something \Nwith the power we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.43,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,We will defeat Ieyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.39,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.86,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura, the next time we meet \Nwill be on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.82,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're including \Nme in your numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:39.91,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the real treasure was not \Nthe Kushimitama, but the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:44.12,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Sanada Yukimura. \NYou are not to be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.62,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,But, even if we know \Nwhat the treasure is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.33,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,we must still be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.79,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,Masamune-sama, where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.55,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,We'll attack head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.41,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take on Ishida Mitsunari, \NNaoe Kanetsugu, and all the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.80,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to start a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.76,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,A big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.39,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to shake the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.37,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it never even happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.98,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.35,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You promised we'd go until I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.94,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.78,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Kamanosuke's quite obsessed with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.46,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,But Kamanosuke's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.49,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami won't stop whining \Nwhen you're not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.93,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.87,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:53.83,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you gather us knowing \Nwhat would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.80,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,How could I predict such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:59.63,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of answer is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.21,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.85,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,If you had told us before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.47,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Could you have stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:10.68,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,More will come seeking her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.40,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It may cost us more next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:14.86,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.95,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to \Nhandle it when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.00,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's all on the braves, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.77,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We're just like pawns in the \Npalm of your hand, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.74,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.87,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.70,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can do is believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:37.67,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I may be another pawn \Nmoved by an unseen power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:41.96,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Some large power like a civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.76,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.93,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Manju, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.66,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you bring so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.68,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you each going to eat ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.30,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.65,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:01.11,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ten times eleven is 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.72,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.20,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any limits?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.33,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.88,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I made these for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.18,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just say thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:12.65,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.40,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You can be so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.13,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.94,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, how dare \Nyou insult Isanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.51,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, the tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:22.35,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you spill it, I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.56,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.69,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,These are delicious.\NMiss, these are really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:27.86,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.43,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them every day from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.73,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on snack duty starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.29,Brave-Main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Snack duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.33,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.94,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You each have your own duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.69,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You decided for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.96,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ben-chan, your job's heating the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.19,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.69,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.03,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't side with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.95,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you're on strong duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.60,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.99,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.86,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakei-san, you'll make the beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:55.91,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.22,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:59.62,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kamanosuke, your job's to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:00.81,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:01.96,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Amaharu is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:02.92,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Squirmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:04.19,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.19,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Give him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:06.24,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:08.89,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I worked hard on these.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:12.09,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:15.70,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,But we will need a captain \Nfor the ten of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:17.49,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakei-san, why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:18.85,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:21.37,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I make frequent trips away from Ueda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:23.58,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:26.67,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monkey, so ruling this mountain \Nshould be right up his alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:30.99,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so short tempered!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:31.83,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.45,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? Get ready, you monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.91,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,No, prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.63,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:43.55,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.51,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I am not the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.32,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:51.23,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,That is your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:51.89,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:55.35,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that why you got mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.06,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Do not say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:04.50,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:05.44,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:06.91,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.88,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:11.32,Brave-Main,JINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.71,0:23:14.48,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.25,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:20.37,Brave-Fin,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Fin.
